核心能力 Competence
■ 運用基礎科學理論探究事物本質的能力。(能力一)
 Possess the ability to apply fundamental scientific theory to explore the essence of things.
■ 運用專業工程素養，設計製程單元、整合並組織系統的能力。(能力二)
 Possess the ability to utilize engineering professional, design process units, integrate and organize systems.
□ 設計與執行實驗，以及分析與解釋數據的能力。(能力三)
 Possess the ability to design and execute experiments, and analyze and interpret data.
□ 具備使用現代工具及執行工程實務所需技術、技巧的能力。(能力四)
 Possess the expertise and skill for utilizing modern tools and executing engineering practices.
■ 具備口頭與撰寫報告、有效溝通、領域整合及團隊合作的能力。(能力五)
 Possess the ability to give presentations, write reports, communicate effectively, integrate different fields, and work with others as a team.
□ 發掘、分析、應用研究成果及處理複雜且整合性工程問題的能力。(能力六)
 Possess the ability to discover, analyze, apply research results, and handle complex and integrated engineering problems.
□ 理解及應用專業倫理，認知社會責任及尊重多元觀點 (能力七)
 Apprehend and apply professional ethics, acknowledge societal responsibility, and respect diversified perspectives.
□ 認識時勢變遷，瞭解工程技術對環境、社會及全球的影響，並培養終身學習成長的習慣。(能力八)
 Understand the changes in the modern world, understand the influence of the engineering technology on the environment, society, and earth, and cultivate the habit on lifelong learning.
 

課程概述 Course Description
       化學感測器概論
1. Overview of sensing technology and its terminology (3 h)
2. Electrochemical sensors (12 h)
  a. Basics of electrochemistry
  b. Introduction to modified electrode
c. Types of electrochemical sensors (amperometric sensor, potentiometric sensor, voltammetric sensors)
3. Chemiresistive chemosensor (9 h)
a. Basics of semiconductor
b. Chemiresistive chemosensor and its working principle
4. Midterm exam (3 h)
5. Optical sensors (6 h)
  a. Colorimetric chemosensor and its working principle
  b. Other optical based devices
6. Mass sensitive devices (6 h)
  a. piezoelectric devices and its working principle
  b. surface acoustic wave devices and its working principle
7. Thermometric sensors and its working principle (3 h)
8. Introduction to biosensors (6 h)
    

課程學習目標 Course Objectives    
	    1.瞭解    

課程進度 Course Outline


週次 Week進度說明 Progress Description
1Overview of sensing technology and its terminology2Electrochemical sensors_Basics of electrochemistry I3Electrochemical sensors-Basics of electrochemistry II410/10 Holliday5Electrochemical sensors-modes of electrochemistry transduction I6Electrochemical sensors-modes of electrochemistry transduction II7Biosensors-Enzyme and enzymatic sensors I8Biosensors-Enzyme and enzymatic sensors II9Biosensors-Applications10Chemiresistive chemosensor-Fundamental of semiconductor11Chemiresistive chemosensor-Applications12Midterm exam13Optical sensors I: Fundamental14Optical sensors II: Applications15Microcantilever sensors16Thermochemical sensors17Lab on chip18Final oral report 

　以上每週進度教師可依上課情況做適度調整。The schedule may be subject to change.


